== Campaign Overview ==
Welcome to the Nuremberg Campaign, a detailed AD&D 2E setting set in the Holy Roman Empire during the early 15th century. This guide will help you navigate the rich historical and cultural tapestry of Nuremberg, a free imperial city at the crossroads of trade, religion, and politics.

